# ========================================
# Admin Panel Security Notes
# ========================================
# 1. Use strong passwords with special characters, numbers, and mixed case
# 2. Role Types:
#    - super_admin: Full access to all markets and administrative functions
#    - market_admin: Access only to specified market data
# 3. Market Access:
#    - Use "all" for super_admin role to access all markets
#    - Use specific market names (Ramanagara, Kollegala, etc.) for market_admin
# 4. Session Duration: 8 hours (configured in adminAuth.ts)
# 5. Failed Login Protection: 3 attempts max, then 5-minute lockout

# ========================================
# Password Security Recommendations
# ========================================
# - Minimum 12 characters
# - Include uppercase and lowercase letters
# - Include numbers and special characters
# - Avoid common words or patterns
# - Use unique passwords for each admin account
#
# Example strong password format:
# AppName@Year!Market (e.g., Reshme@2025!Rama)

# ========================================
# Firebase Security Setup Required
# ========================================
# After setting up your environment variables, you need to:
# 1. Update Firestore Security Rules:
#    - Copy rules from firestore.rules.admin
#    - Deploy to Firebase Console > Firestore > Rules
# 2. Optional: Enable Firebase Authentication for enhanced security
# 3. Test admin panel access in development mode

# ========================================
# Development vs Production
# ========================================
# Development:
# - Admin panel access via shield icon (üõ°Ô∏è) in top-right corner
# - Fallback hardcoded credentials available for testing
#
# Production:
# - Shield icon automatically hidden
# - Only environment variable credentials accepted
# - Consider additional security measures (IP restrictions, etc.)

# ========================================
# Troubleshooting
# ========================================
# Common Issues:
# 1. "Invalid credentials" - Check username/password spelling
# 2. "Permission denied" - Verify Firestore rules are updated
# 3. "Session expired" - Sessions last 8 hours, login again
# 4. "Market access denied" - Check ADMIN_MARKET_X configuration
#
# For support: Check ADMIN_PANEL_README.md for detailed documentation

